                <div class="president-message">
                    <p>"I warmly welcome you all as we begin another year of dedication and service to our institution. As student representatives, we have the responsibility to foster a dynamic, inclusive campus that promotes growth, innovation, and collaboration.</p>
                    
                    <p>Your commitment is essential in driving meaningful initiatives, addressing student concerns, and enriching academic and extracurricular experiences. I encourage each of you to actively contribute, share insights, and work together toward our shared vision of excellence.</p>
                    
                    <p>Let's uphold leadership, integrity, and service as we strive to make a lasting impact on our college community. I look forward to working alongside you all to achieve our common goals."</p>
                </div>

                
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
